Revision history for AIO-Celery

0.01  2026-03-27
    - Initial release
    - Full Celery Message Protocol v2 implementation
    - RabbitMQ broker via Net::Async::AMQP
    - Redis result backend via Net::Async::Redis
    - Async worker with configurable concurrency (IO::Async + Future::AsyncAwait)
    - Task chaining via Canvas signatures
    - Task retry with configurable backoff
    - HTTP inspection server for monitoring
    - CLI worker: aio-celery worker Module::Name:variable
    - Full interoperability with Python Celery/aio-celery
